{"tid":1623104,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"大家裝修黨鐵站可唔可以對準黨鐵同美心","createTime":"2019-10-04T18:23:55.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-04T18:39:41.000Z","uid":304052,"like":1,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"2444173b481a9ecdeeac263753fa39f1291845af","tid":1623104,"uid":304052,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T18:23:55.000Z","msg":"我知我係P 牌，自己屌自己一次先<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n想同各位手足講，我100% 支持裝修行動，亦都好憎黨鐵。<br />\n但有一件事想拜託大家<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n可唔可以對準黨鐵同美心/藍舖？譬如客服呀月台呀嗰啲？<br />\n因為屋企人有喺黨鐵站租舖頭（幾年前簽左㗎喇，嗰陣黨鐵仲未係黨鐵，同屋企人係全部深黃，會去遊行集會接放學買物資 etc.)，今晚有啲站流口水，浸埋成間舖<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我地雖然都唔開心，但明白手足唔係有心，亦一定一定唔會割蓆，但希望下次裝修可以諗一諗，針對返賣港嘅舖頭先<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n最後祝各位武運昌隆，萬事小心唔洗俾狗咬<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"157ec9f4c04707849cc04e6573eaa2526e91c173","tid":1623104,"uid":28831,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T18:25:27.000Z","msg":"流口水冇計架wor<br />\n唔通仲入去逐間拆咩"},{"pid":"9dc80871cac6500f096bf19851f77f212cf295db","tid":1623104,"uid":304052,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"157ec9f4c04707849cc04e6573eaa2526e91c173","tid":1623104,"uid":28831,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T18:25:27.000Z","msg":"流口水冇計架wor<br />\n唔通仲入去逐間拆咩"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T18:28:56.000Z","msg":"我都明<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />但屋企人入面係有銀髮族，真係身體力行支持呢場運動㗎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />佢見到舖頭都浸埋聽日又要去執手尾，大家盡量就下好唔好......"},{"pid":"520d921df206b4749949150b09177b4302b3bbc5","tid":1623104,"uid":50122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T18:32:22.000Z","msg":"玩水留意返